snippet.title: Dachs Hunter - Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Dachs Hunter is a top-down roguelite game where you play as a Dachshund Wizard and survive the hordes of elemental monsters. Discover and collect unique spells, create game-breaking synergies while mastering all the elements. 

Wishlist now on Steam!
